div.p: Grottesco: in diversche manieren / Zeer Chierlijck bequaem en oirboorlijc / voor Schilders Glasschrijuers, Beeldsnijders / En al die de Chierlijcke ornamenten der / Antiquen beminnen, ghemackt by / Iohans Vredeman Vries, wth ghegheuen / duer Geraert de Ieude,

Groteques: in diverse ways, very decorative, skilled, and useful for painters, glass-writers, sculptors, and all those who love the decorative ornaments of the ancients, made by Johan Vredeman de Vries, published by Gerard de Jode.
